Index.title: LoLStudio2 Launcher
Index.subtitle: Version 2.3.0.6.5, 2013-04-30
Index.text:
V2.3.0.6.5 Lissandra -Data update for patch 3.6. This includes the new hero Lissandra. -Also included are the reworked heroes Trundle and Sejuani. -A million other things.
V2.3.0.6.4 Zac -Data update for patch 3.5. This includes the new hero Zac and the reworked hero Karma.
V2.3.0.6.3 Quinn -Data update for patch 3.04.
V2.3.0.6.2 Quinn -Data update for patch 3.03. This includes Quinn and Valor the new champion tag team.
V2.3.0.6.1 Season 3 -LoLStudio now has multiple GUI themes and a much requested dark skin (well, I requested it) -I removed the option to set your own data directory because it was worthless anyway -Rewrote some of the launcher code to reduce the update file size and make it more reliable -As a result, the launcher will no longer preserve stuff you have edited manually by hand -Added the ability to update the launcher itself which should make things easier in the future
